            </ul>

            <h3>{{t "3. Acceptable Use Policy" key="terms_acceptable_use_heading"}}</h3>
            <p>{{t "You agree not to:" key="terms_acceptable_use_intro"}}</p>
            <ul>
              <li>{{t "Use the Service for any illegal or unauthorized purpose." key="terms_acceptable_use_1"}}</li>
              <li>{{t "Upload viruses, malicious code, or attempt to breach our security systems." key="terms_acceptable_use_2"}}</li>
              <li>{{t "Infringe upon the intellectual property rights of others when uploading custom images or audio." key="terms_acceptable_use_3"}}</li>
            </ul>

            <h3>{{t "4. Limitation of Liability (Protecting LingoLinq)" key="terms_liability_heading"}}</h3>
            <p>{{t "TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW, LINGOLINQ LLC SHALL NOT BE LIABLE FOR ANY INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL, CONSEQUENTIAL, OR PUNITIVE DAMAGES, OR ANY LOSS OF PROFITS OR REVENUES, WHETHER INCURRED DIRECTLY OR INDIRECTLY, OR ANY LOSS OF DATA, USE, GOODWILL, OR OTHER INTANGIBLE LOSSES, RESULTING FROM (A) YOUR ACCESS TO OR USE OF OR INABILITY TO ACCESS OR USE THE SERVICE; (B) ANY UNAUTHORIZED ACCESS TO OR USE OF OUR SECURE SERVERS AND/OR ANY PERSONAL INFORMATION STORED THEREIN." key="terms_liability"}}</p>

            <h3>{{t "5. Force Majeure" key="terms_force_majeure_heading"}}</h3>
            <p>{{t "LingoLinq shall not be liable for any failure or delay in performance under these Terms due to circumstances beyond our reasonable control, including but not limited to acts of God, natural disasters, cyber warfare, systemic internet outages, or government actions." key="terms_force_majeure"}}</p>

            <h3>{{t "6. Termination" key="terms_termination_heading"}}</h3>
            <p>{{t "We reserve the right to suspend or terminate your account at any time, with or without cause, if you violate these Terms. You may terminate your account at any time via your account settings." key="terms_termination"}}</p>

            <h3>{{t "7. Contact Us" key="terms_contact_heading"}}</h3>
            <p>{{t "If you have questions about these Terms or the Service, please contact us:" key="terms_contact_intro"}}</p>
            <p class="la-privacy-address">
              {{t "Email:" key="privacy_contact_email_label"}} <a href="mailto:support@lingolinq.com">support@lingolinq.com</a><br>
              {{t "Phone:" key="privacy_contact_phone_label"}} (801) 739-5307<br>
              {{t "Mail:" key="privacy_contact_mail_label"}} LingoLinq LLC, 5041 Taylor Ave, Ogden, UT 84403
            </p>

            <p>{{t "© 2026 LingoLinq LLC. All rights reserved." key="privacy_copyright"}}</p>
